    ((sp_500_index_2017 - sp_500_index_2018) / sp_500_index_2017 - (jpmorgan_chase_stock_price_2017 - jpmorgan_chase_stock_price_2018) / jpmorgan_chase_stock_price_2017) * 100 AS variation
FROM (
    SELECT 
        year, 
        jpmorgan_chase_stock_price, 
        sp_500_index, 
        (jpmorgan_chase_stock_price - LAG(jpmorgan_chase_stock_price) OVER (ORDER BY year)) / LAG(jpmorgan_chase_stock_price) OVER (ORDER BY year) AS jpmorgan_chase_stock_price_decrease,
        (sp_500_index - LAG(sp_500_index) OVER (ORDER BY year)) / LAG(sp_500_index) OVER (ORDER BY year) AS sp_500_index_decrease
    FROM JPMorganChasePerformance
) AS subquery
WHERE year IN (2017, 2018);
SELECT increase_rate FROM PreD WHERE year = 2010 - 1
SELECT SUM(CASE WHEN T1.obligation_type = 'Long-term debt' THEN T1.total ELSE 0 END) / SUM(T1.total) AS long_term_debt_percentage FROM FIS_Contractual_Obligations AS T1
SELECT CAST(unrecognized_compensation_expense_rsrs AS REAL) / unrecognized_compensation_expense_rpsrs FROM PreD WHERE year = 2011 AND month = 12
SELECT (debt_to_capital - LAG(debt_to_capital) OVER (ORDER BY year)) / LAG(debt_to_capital) OVER (ORDER BY year) * 100 AS percent_change FROM DebtToCapital WHERE year IN (2012, 2013)
SELECT range_start, range_end FROM TableData WHERE year IN (2013, 2014)
SELECT T1.capital_plan * T2.ptc_expenditures / 100 FROM PostD AS T1 JOIN PreD AS T2 ON 1=1 WHERE T1.year = 2015
SELECT (T1.accumulated_other_comprehensive_loss - T2.balance_in_aocl) AS net_change FROM TableData AS T1 INNER JOIN UnrealizedLosses AS T2 ON T1.year = T2.year WHERE T1.year = 2009 AND T2.year = 2008
SELECT (LC.federal * (1 - (SELECT excess_tax_benefits / valuation_allowance FROM PreD WHERE year = 2010))) / LC.federal FROM LossCarryForwards AS LC WHERE LC.year = 2010
SELECT SUM(benefit_amount) FROM BenefitData WHERE year = 2007
SELECT T1.license_expiration - T2.inserviceyear AS lease_length FROM PowerPlants AS T2 JOIN EntergyWholesaleCommodities AS T1 ON T2.name = T1.organization_name WHERE T1.organization_name = 'Pilgrim'
SELECT (total_net_of_cash_collateral_2018 - total_net_of_cash_collateral_2017) * 1000000 FROM CollateralData WHERE year = 2018 AS T1 JOIN CollateralData AS T2 ON T1.year = T2.year - 1
SELECT CAST(SUM(CASE WHEN payment_period LIKE '1 year' THEN total ELSE 0 END) AS REAL) * 100 / SUM(total) FROM ContractualCashObligations
